&lt;First Philadelphia Corp> said itsComputone Systems Inc unit filed a chapter 11 plan for with theU.S. Bankruptcy Court in Atlanta.    Subject to confirmation by the court of the plan, theassets of Computone's two operating divisions would betransferred to CPX Inc, a wholly-owned subsidiary of FirstPhiladelphia, the company said.    First Philadelphia said it is in the process of raising1,750,000 dlrs to complement it initial investment of 750,000dlrs to fund the cost of the reorganization and provide ongoingcapital for existing Computone businesses. Reuter&#3;